Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起  拉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come on. Everyone -- pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你要出门吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hey. Going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得找回马\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We need to get our horses back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你进来时看见东墙了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You see the east wall when you came in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天该帮忙的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You were marked down to help today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你似乎已经有一队人了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Looks like you've got a crew already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你一早都不见人影\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, you were gone all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就先开工了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We started without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  亚伦  我今天没法帮你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sorry, Aaron. I can't today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你在追踪一群\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Because you're tracking horses
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎没希望抓到的马吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that you have almost no hope of catching?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,达里尔和我之前也这样做过\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know, Daryl and I went down that road before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,最后也没抓到巴顿斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Didn't work out so well for Buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的口粮快没了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We're almost out of MREs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,庄稼地就是个笑话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and the fields are a joke --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的墙要不行了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And our walls are about to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们找不到马\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, if we don't get those horses,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就没法搬运比一袋粮食\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}we're not gonna be able to move anything heavier
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,更重的东西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}than a sack of grain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也没法去远方搜刮物资\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Or go out far enough to scavenge anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都会饿死的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and we're all gonna starve to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我几小时后回来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So I'll be back in a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很饿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm hungry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈出去时  你会担心吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do you ever worry about your mom when she goes away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我都习惯了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大人总是会出去办事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Grown-ups are always running off doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"我保证会很快回来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"Promise I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你哦"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在旧时代他们常说那种话  对吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They used to say that kind of stuff in the olden times, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在没法保证  但还是这样说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They can't promise it now, but they say it anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不希望我们认为他们再也回不来了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They don't want us to think they're never coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那些话是为了让我们好受些\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's supposed to make us feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是为了让自己好受些\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They say it to make themselvesfeel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈总是会回来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}my mom always comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Dang it.
