Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,计划不变\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The plan doesn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要那些食物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We need that food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去无线电塔  找到补给屋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We get to the radio tower, find the supply house,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,然后等待其他人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and wait for the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果其他人死了呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And what if the others are dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解戏剧效果\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Listen, I know theatrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人刚告诉了我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Those people, they just told us
