Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能走任何他们可能走的路\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We can't be on any road that they could use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个糟糕的计划\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's a shit plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那你告诉我一个更好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Then you tell me a better one
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让我们所有人饿死的计划\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that doesn't starve us all.
