Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是站在你这边的  玛姬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I am on your side, Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那就帮我带他走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Then help me with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,二  三  起\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}2, 3, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
