Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-你没事吧  -没事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- You good? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只是加百利在执行任务\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, it's just that Gabriel's on a mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而我被困在家里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I'm over being stuck in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  你们在做什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Why? What're you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,第四次准有好运气\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Fourth time's the charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们继续吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let's get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,等抓到马就没事了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'll be better when this is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我最近一直在做关于亚伯拉罕的梦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've been having dreams about Abraham recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  他想告诉我某件事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, he's trying to tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道那是重要的事  我应该做的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know it's something important, something I'm supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但大部分时候我都听不见他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But I can't hear him most of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就当我快听见时\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and just when I'm about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他就被爆头了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}he, um -- he gets shot in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真阴暗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, that's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我不知道我为什么告诉你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, I don't know why I just told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我懂的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,以前这会让我恐慌\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It used to freak me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我觉得这是一条给我们和亚历山大的信息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but now I think it's a message for us, for Alexandria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他想说什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What do you think he's trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果马让你摸它的耳朵\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know, if a horse lets you touch its ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就代表它信任你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}it means it trusts you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我读到过\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I read that once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我们能把它们抓回来吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You think we'll get them back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,马是野性的动物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Horses are wild creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很难说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有两英里  比我想的要更远\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's 2 miles. It's further than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那就快走吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We better get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,牵着你的手并不会帮我走快一点\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Holding your hand's not gonna help me walk any faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  那想到那些行尸会撕下你的脸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah? Does the thought of one of those things
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮你走快点吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}ripping your face off do it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你害怕  为什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If you're scared, why don't you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不发挥下作用  去杀死它们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}make yourself useful and go kill 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗  我们要朝着尖叫声走吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Really? So we're just gonna go towards the screaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,阿加莎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Agatha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,玛姬  邓肯出事了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maggie. It's Duncan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,邓肯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Duncan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,邓肯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Duncan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为所有事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}For all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之前过得很好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We were good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很幸运\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We were lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,持续了一小段时间\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}For a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,确保她平安回家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Make sure she gets home.
