Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这边走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
