Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们继续找其它的马\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We'll keep looking for the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,它们会待在水源附近\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They'll stay close to the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果到处是尸体它们就不会了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not if it's full of corpses they won't.
