Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她说得对\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没必要现在去找\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We don't have to do this right now.
