Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不  亚历山大昨天就需要这些马\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, Alexandria needed these horses yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,卡萝尔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Carol...
