Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再试试\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We'll try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,下一次\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也许不用了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maybe not.
