Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张  别紧张\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Easy now. Easy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,放下套索\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Drop the lassos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Why?
