Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.48,0:33:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前吃过吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You've eaten it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.56,0:33:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  跟我妈妈漂泊时吃过\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, on the road, with my mom.
