Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.95,0:33:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,快点嚼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just chew it fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.62,0:33:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么难吃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.00,0:33:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没蜘蛛难吃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not like the spiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.59,0:33:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,想不想摸小马\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Wanna see if we can pet a pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.72,0:33:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.56,0:33:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,它们有兴趣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They're interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.94,0:34:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你想摸小马吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do you want to pet a pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.23,0:34:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧  快看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Beautiful, right? Look. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.42,0:35:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.60,0:35:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈恶心\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Goddamn shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.23,0:35:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.07,0:35:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吃烂纸板吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You like the taste of crap cardboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.70,0:35:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该回到树林里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We should get back in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.37,0:35:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,走大路更快\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The road is faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.37,0:35:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他说得对  树林里有掩护  更安全\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's right. The woods have cover. It's safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.71,0:35:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去那里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let's go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.71,0:35:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.88,0:35:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得继续前进\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We need to keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.71,0:35:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我们得休息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, we need a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.37,0:36:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里休息一下  然后出发\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We'll rest here for a while, and then we'll head out.
