Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.01,0:36:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,回答是不行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.85,0:36:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他是对的  玛姬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's right, Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.18,0:36:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我拖累你们了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm slowing you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.48,0:36:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.40,0:36:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.61,0:36:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也许现在没事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maybe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.94,0:36:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那些人和你所说的一样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If these guys are anything like you say they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.90,0:37:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,情况就会变得更糟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}then it's gonna get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.83,0:37:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个累赘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm dead weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.66,0:37:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We all know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.04,0:37:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会帮你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.30,0:37:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道我为什么离开了他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You wanna know why I walked away from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.93,0:37:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,和他所代表的一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and everything he stood for...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.85,0:37:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,加入了你吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}joined up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.56,0:37:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我信任你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's 'cause I trust you...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.65,0:37:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能做正确的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.32,0:37:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有多难  要付出多大代价\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No matter how hard it is or how much it costs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.45,0:37:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,补给  玛姬  看着我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The supplies -- Maggie, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.16,0:37:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,补给是现在唯一重要的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The supplies are the only thing that matters now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.25,0:37:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历山大需要我们取回补给\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Alexandria needs us to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.46,0:37:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在等着我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They're waiting for us.
