Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.43,0:38:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Adam...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.30,0:38:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当需要一个父亲\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And Adam needs a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.18,0:38:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我这样能活着离开那个镇子吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You think I'm gonna make it out of that town alive like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.68,0:38:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你丢下了盖奇  也丢下我吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You left Gage. Leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.31,0:38:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,盖奇做出了选择\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Gage made his choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.44,0:38:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也做出了选择\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And I'm making mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.11,0:38:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.57,0:38:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.41,0:38:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.99,0:38:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,玛姬  如果这个计划失败了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maggie, if this plan fails...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.24,0:38:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那你所为之奋斗的一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}then everything you've worked for,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.12,0:38:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你对未来的一切愿景\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}everything you want for the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.00,0:38:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,都会破灭\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}it dies with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.80,0:38:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然后亚当会怎样呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And then what happens to Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.72,0:38:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.88,0:38:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么简单\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.60,0:38:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么简单\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, it is.
