Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.16,0:39:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,全然不顾别人的性命\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Being reckless with somebody else's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.29,0:39:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但别人的生死现在不由你决定了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But you don't get to decide who lives and who dies anymore.
