Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.27,0:40:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,玛姬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Ma-- Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.07,0:40:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Here.
